## When Stuck

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Don't know which table owns data | Check `db/radio.schema.sql` for column locations |
| Query returns wrong columns | Verify JOINs follow FK relationships in schema |
| Interface doesn't compile | Match interface to schema column types exactly |
| JSONB seems necessary | List all fields - if predictable, make columns |
| Need synthetic id | Verify no natural key exists (composite or FK) |
| Existing code violates rules | Fix this instance - don't propagate violations |
| Mapper seems complex | Create mapping table first (source.path → column) |
| Source has nested fields | Trace each nested path to its schema column |
| Schema columns are NULL | Compare source type to schema - find missing extraction |
| Not sure which fields to map | Map ALL fields that have schema columns - no exceptions |

## Final Rule

```
Schema change → validate against DRY, PK design, JSONB, FK rules
Query → validate against db/radio.schema.sql
Interface → must mirror schema exactly
Otherwise → violation → fix before proceeding
```

No exceptions without human partner's permission.

